  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our Community!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/96c2ecb09708c7bf6e1a050776511232.avif?t=1748340291\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>Grimlord</strong> - a <strong>Dark Fantasy Action Souls-like RPG</strong> built on <strong>Unreal Engine 5</strong> for VR. Awakened in a monastery deep in the Lonely Mountains, you walk in an epic quest as the adventurer standing before the darkness and striving for the light against the tyrannical Grim Lord.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/b7a1941b67233d8a51be5e6be7d927cf.avif?t=1748340291\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras_big/b7a1941b67233d8a51be5e6be7d927cf.avif?t=1748340291 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/03d8613f44b0f924d34750f868134c31.webp?t=1748340291\" width=600 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/ff6c8e512a6cc4faeb97572f3c785d54.poster.avif?t=1748340291\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/ff6c8e512a6cc4faeb97572f3c785d54.webm?t=1748340291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/ff6c8e512a6cc4faeb97572f3c785d54.mp4?t=1748340291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re a prisoner in a monastery somewhere deep in the Lonely Mountains. You are free to choose how to fight your way out. Choose your way of becoming a battling adventurer whilst standing before the darkness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/03d8613f44b0f924d34750f868134c31.webp?t=1748340291\" width=600 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/2a09085f542e7cdda2adf5d01e13632d.poster.avif?t=1748340291\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/2a09085f542e7cdda2adf5d01e13632d.webm?t=1748340291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/2a09085f542e7cdda2adf5d01e13632d.mp4?t=1748340291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grimlord brings combat in VR like never before. With a ton of unique enemies sprawling the monastery grounds capable of showing you their individual combat prowess, you’re left to learn how to deal with them efficiently - for survival’s sake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/03d8613f44b0f924d34750f868134c31.webp?t=1748340291\" width=600 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/e181f8da96b05e8fb13314b65d27258a.poster.avif?t=1748340291\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/e181f8da96b05e8fb13314b65d27258a.webm?t=1748340291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/e181f8da96b05e8fb13314b65d27258a.mp4?t=1748340291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you a battle-hardened sword & shield adventurer or a staff-wielding magic artist? Maybe a long-ranged bow & arrow assassin? How about an agile dual-wielding bladesman? Even go wild as a shield & dagger throwing specialist? The choice is yours, prisoner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/03d8613f44b0f924d34750f868134c31.webp?t=1748340291\" width=600 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/18ba82f71bedc1b9d4004a8811175ca0.poster.avif?t=1748340291\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/18ba82f71bedc1b9d4004a8811175ca0.webm?t=1748340291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/18ba82f71bedc1b9d4004a8811175ca0.mp4?t=1748340291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/47dfe8ccd9115ae89647cd9e540165c7.poster.avif?t=1748340291\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/47dfe8ccd9115ae89647cd9e540165c7.webm?t=1748340291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/47dfe8ccd9115ae89647cd9e540165c7.mp4?t=1748340291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With boss battles meant to test your accumulated skills and knowledge, each encounter assures every prisoner’s adventure to strive for the light is as unique as it can be.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>Grimlord</strong> - a <strong>Dark Fantasy Action Souls-like RPG</strong> built on <strong>Unreal Engine 5</strong> for VR. Awakened in a monastery deep in the Lonely Mountains, you walk in an epic quest as the adventurer standing before the darkness and striving for the light against the tyrannical Grim Lord.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/b7a1941b67233d8a51be5e6be7d927cf.avif?t=1748340291\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras_big/b7a1941b67233d8a51be5e6be7d927cf.avif?t=1748340291 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/03d8613f44b0f924d34750f868134c31.webp?t=1748340291\" width=600 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/ff6c8e512a6cc4faeb97572f3c785d54.poster.avif?t=1748340291\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/ff6c8e512a6cc4faeb97572f3c785d54.webm?t=1748340291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910860/extras/ff6c8e512a6cc4faeb97572f3c785d54.mp4?t=1748340291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re a prisoner in a monastery somewhere deep in the Lonely Mountains. You are free to choose how to fight your way out. Choose your way of becoming a battling adventurer whilst standing before the darkness.</p><p class=\"bb_p